Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: m. k. e. flavors
des:
How would you like to get frozen custard flavor of the day information for locations throughout the Milwaukee area? If so, this skill is for you! We update daily with 40+ locations throughout the greater Milwaukee area. 

You can ask:

"Alexa, ask MKE Flavors for the flavors near me?" 
"Alexa, open MKE Flavors and ask for the flavor at <Location Name>"

To access the flavors near you, please make sure to allow location services when enabling this skill.
